São Pedro do Sul, Viseu, Portugal

The house is located in the center of the village of Várzea de Abrunhais, 5 km from the spa of S. Pedro do Sul. It is a very quiet place, ideal for rest and relaxation. The house has a large garden with fruit trees and a small vegetable garden. The house is fully equipped and has a barbecue.
